    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/633bc3c0db463d60b46e4fe844be4460.avif?t=1758281238\" width=599 height=148 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/9b3c4daf8f556a04bd545d385d3ff78f.webp?t=1758281238\" width=610 height=6 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索被遗忘国度的纠葛</strong></h2><br>在低语海洋的吞噬之臂间，建立在过于雄心勃勃梦想之上的雾角岛国，如今已沦为废墟。王座空虚，大地淹没在污秽、虚荣和令人毛骨悚然的恐惧之中。<br><br>《Crave》是一款经典风格的2D动作冒险游戏，带你穿越广阔而相互连接的世界。利用你的食肉动物兵器库，探索这衰败国度的曲折小巷和角落。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/764bafdf96a0989c3442fbc2f18c308c.poster.avif?t=1758281238\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/764bafdf96a0989c3442fbc2f18c308c.webm?t=1758281238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/764bafdf96a0989c3442fbc2f18c308c.mp4?t=1758281238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/9b3c4daf8f556a04bd545d385d3ff78f.webp?t=1758281238\" width=610 height=6 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏亮点</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 经典2D横版动作冒险游戏。<br></li><li> 精调操作手感，带来富挑战性的战斗与平台跳跃体验。 <br></li><li>  探索布满苔藓的浴室、歌舞厅剧院或发霉温室，穿梭于广阔相连的世界。 <br></li><li> 重新发掘并运用你作为食肉动物的能力，战斗探索无往不利。  <br></li><li> 吞噬对手，无论人兽。将其能力为己所用。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/df26a1268f07de907f65e4dd43df9259.poster.avif?t=1758281238\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/df26a1268f07de907f65e4dd43df9259.webm?t=1758281238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/df26a1268f07de907f65e4dd43df9259.mp4?t=1758281238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>  凭借敏锐嗅觉与标记领地的排尿能力，绘制王国布局。 <br></li><li>  装备小饰品与护身符，自定义游戏风格。 <br></li><li>  手绘2D传统动画风格。<br></li><li>  由Sky to Speak创作的原创回味配乐。 </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/d23b8ca6abe2a1c1008596a97fc82cf1.poster.avif?t=1758281238\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/d23b8ca6abe2a1c1008596a97fc82cf1.webm?t=1758281238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/9b3c4daf8f556a04bd545d385d3ff78f.webp?t=1758281238\" width=610 height=6 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏由Slovak Arts Council公共资金支持。</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/51c4fa54c217cd926ee516147f10f25c.avif?t=1758281238\" width=200 height=73 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826400/extras/9b3c4daf8f556a04bd545d385d3ff78f.webp?t=1758281238\" width=610 height=6 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入我们的Discord社区！</strong></h2><br>",
